name: DumbDex
0:

”Alexa, ask Dumb Dex to tell me about Mewtwo”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dumb dex
des:
Use Dumb Dex to get the Pokedex entries on your favorite Pokemon. Just ask Alexa to describe or tell you about a specific Pokemon, and she will reply with a Pokedex entry from one of the games! More features will be added soon such as: stats, evolutions, and types!
Currently restricted to Generation 1.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
